  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time video and voice AI with WebRTC support",
    "Ultra-low latency (<30ms) using Stream's edge network",
    "Plugin architecture with 37+ integrations (OpenAI, Gemini, AWS, etc.)",
    "Flexible processor pipeline for custom video/audio processing",
    "Native support for YOLO, Roboflow, and custom vision models",
    "Built-in turn detection, VAD, and speech-to-speech pipelines",
    "Function calling and tool use during conversations",
    "Session management with in-memory and Redis stores",
    "Production-ready HTTP API deployment",
    "Comprehensive observability with metrics and telemetry"
